{"title":"Minnie Small Plush with Sounds","description":"

Disney Minnie Small Plush with Sounds

Bring home these adorable Disney Classics Mickey Mouse small plush toys. With their sweet disposition and expressive, embroidered eyes, these huggable stuffed animals will win the hearts of Disney fans of all ages. Made of super-soft mixed materials for the ultimate in snuggle-ability, these plushies are perfect for nap time, story time, bedtime, and play. They even feature fun sound effects! At 10 inches tall, the plush pals make great companions for toddlers on the go. Collect all the characters in the assortment, including Mickey Mouse, Minnie Mouse, Donald Duck, and Daisy Duck. Each sold separately and requires 3xAG13 batteries (included). For kids ages 2 years and up.

  • Height: 178 MM

  • And at 10 inches tall, kids will love to bring it along for on-the-go playtime
  • Great for play or display.
  • Requires 3 x AG13 batteries.
  • Makes a great gift for kids ages 2 years and up.
